<div class="sec">
  <h3 class="sectitle">Research Interests</h3>
  <div class="sec">
  <div class="secbody">
   Natural language processing, machine learning, 
  artificial intelligence, and human computer interaction.
  </div></div>

  <h3 class="sectitle">Recent Publications</h3>
  <div class="sec">  
  <div class="secbody">

Huichao Xue and Rebecca Hwa. 2014. Improved Correction Detection in Revised ESL Sentences. In The Proceedings of The 52nd Annual Meeting of the Association for Computational Linguistics (ACL short), 2014, Baltimore, Maryland.<br/><br>

Huichao Xue and Rebecca Hwa (2014).Redundancy Detection in ESL Writings. 2014. In the Proceedings of the 14th Conference of the European Chapter of the Association for Computational Linguistics (EACL), Gothenburgh, Sweden. <br/><br> 

Homa Hashemi and Rebecca Hwa. 2014. A Comparison of MT Errors and ESL Errors. In the Proceedings of the 9th edition of the Language Resources and Evaluation Conference (LREC-2014), Reykjavik, Iceland. <br/><br>

